<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/perspective/pv95j2fs.html">Stay Married, Go to 
Church, Live Longer. No Sweat.</a>
<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/perspective/pv95j3ed.html">Education Debate 
Needs to Focus on the Family</a>
<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/perspective/pv95j4wl.html">Reinstate the Family 
Cap in Conference</a>
