<DOCHDR>
http://www.lead-inst.org:80/heritage/p_review/fall95/thhim.html 204.71.237.80 19970217151730 text/html 17375
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 15:18:25 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 17-Nov-95 16:29:25 GMT
Content-length: 17191
