http://www.lead-inst.org:80/heritage/p_review/fall95/thrich.html 204.71.237.80 19970217151737 text/html 11815
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 15:18:35 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 17-Nov-95 16:29:25 GMT
