http://www.lead-inst.org:80/townhall/spotlights/9-18-95/herbudge.html 204.71.237.80 19970210134629 text/html 15611
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 13:47:16 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 20-Oct-95 14:26:46 GMT
