   <p><li> Robbins and Robbins, "Cooking the Books:   Exposing the Tax and Spend Bias of Government Forecasts."  <p><li>  Christopher Frenze, "Capital Gains and the Revenue Estimation Process," <i>Economic Update</i>, Joint Economic Committee, September 1995.  <p><li>  Christopher Frenze, "Massive CBO Errors in Capital Gains Projections," <i>Policy Analysis</i>, Joint Economic Committee, February 1992.
